divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband & I stopped in White Sands, NM on a trip with my sister in May 1995. It was her first visit so she took several photos. We didn't see anything in the sky (or hear anything) when we took the photo & never noticed anything in the photo until I scanned it into the computer today to put on disc. If you zoom in on the photo, you can see another object down to the left above the clouds, but it isn't as surprising as the one I circled.
